@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (View Meetup Details)

start
:1. User selects meetup from list;
:2. System loads meetup details;
:3. System loads participants list;
:4. System loads location info;
:5. Display meetup details screen;

if (User requests to join?) then (Yes)
  :6. Proceed to Join Request flow;
else (No)
  :7. Return or stay on details screen;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Select meetup
2 Load meetup details
3 Load participants
4 Load location info
5 Display details
6 Proceed to join request
7 Return/stay
endlegend

@enduml